"attach" is small wrapper script that helps manage new and existisng screen sessions.

Add the "attach" script to your path, e.g.:
ln -s ${HOME}/src/screen-session-attach/attach ${HOME}/bin/attach

And, if you want tab completion, source the _attach_complete.sh file in your .bashrc, e.g.:
test -r ${HOME}/src/screen-session-attach/_attach_complete.sh && source ${HOME}/src/screen-session-attach/_attach_complete.sh
